%% Xuanwu App — Onboarding Flow
%% New organization / user journey from sign-up to first RAG query

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User / Admin
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth<br/>(identity module)
    participant Account as Account<br/>Module
    participant Org as Organization<br/>Module
    participant WS as Workspace<br/>Module
    participant Content as Content<br/>Module
    participant Asset as Asset<br/>Module
    participant Ingestion as Python Worker<br/>(py_fn)
    participant RAG as Retrieval<br/>Module

    Note over User,RAG: Phase 1 — Account & Organization Setup

    User->>Auth: Sign up (Google / Email)
    Auth-->>Account: uid + profile
    Account->>Account: CreateAccountUseCase
    Account-->>User: Account created ✓

    User->>Org: Create organization
    Org->>Org: CreateOrganizationUseCase
    Org-->>User: Organization created ✓

    Note over User,RAG: Phase 2 — Workspace & Member Onboarding

    User->>WS: Create workspace
    WS->>WS: CreateWorkspaceUseCase
    WS-->>User: Workspace created ✓

    User->>Org: Invite team members
    Org->>Org: InviteMemberUseCase
    Org-->>User: Invitations sent ✓

    Note over User,RAG: Phase 3 — Knowledge Base Setup

    User->>Content: Create first page
    Content->>Content: CreateContentPageUseCase
    Content-->>User: Page created ✓

    User->>Asset: Upload documents (PDF/Word)
    Asset->>Asset: UploadInitFileUseCase
    Asset->>Ingestion: RegisterUploadedRagDocumentUseCase<br/>(creates IngestionJob: uploaded)
    Note right of Ingestion: Parse → Clean → Taxonomy<br/>→ Chunk → Embed → Persist
    Ingestion-->>Asset: IngestionJob status: ready ✓

    Note over User,RAG: Phase 4 — First RAG Query

    User->>RAG: Ask a question
    RAG->>RAG: AnswerRagQueryUseCase<br/>(Vector Search + Genkit)
    RAG-->>User: Answer + Citations ✓

    User->>RAG: Submit feedback (helpful / not helpful)
    RAG->>RAG: SubmitRagQueryFeedbackUseCase
    RAG-->>User: Feedback recorded ✓
